title: Hibino Cafe AGT
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Macrobiotic, Organic, Western, Fusion
description: The restaurant is on the 2nd floor above a shop that sells brown rices, veggies, and organic foodstuff. Reported menu became all-veg (Feb 2016). Offers an array of choices, such as bean burgers and curry. Uses local produce and has sugar-free desserts. Last order is 1 hour before closing.
